WEBVTT

00:08.221 --> 00:12.224
Transcript by Addic7ed.com

00:13.629 --> 00:15.129
Hassan's security forces

00:15.197 --> 00:16.697
in the Islamic Republic

00:16.765 --> 00:17.965
are sweeping
through the capital,

00:18.033 --> 00:19.634
arreing opposition
leaders.

00:19.701 --> 00:23.271
And if he continues, it may
delegitimize the peace accord.

00:23.338 --> 00:25.306
<i>I can't vouch for you</i>

00:25.374 --> 00:26.941
as a reformer, Mr. President,

00:27.009 --> 00:28.409
if you renege

00:28.477 --> 00:30.077
on your human rights
obligations.

00:30.145 --> 00:32.313
My brother tried to kill me,

00:32.381 --> 00:33.981
helped by elements

00:34.049 --> 00:36.083
within my own government.

00:36.151 --> 00:37.652
Apparently,
killing President Hassan

00:37.719 --> 00:39.620
was only part
of his brother's plan.

00:39.688 --> 00:41.455
CTU now believes
he's also trying

00:41.523 --> 00:43.658
to acquire weapons-grade
uranium.

00:43.725 --> 00:45.660
When can I take possession
of the rods?

00:45.727 --> 00:47.662
As soon as we have the money.

00:47.729 --> 00:49.597
<i>JOSEF: I found a doctor
who can treat him.</i>

00:49.665 --> 00:51.132
BAZHAEV:
No doctors.

00:51.199 --> 00:53.100
The authorities know
about the nuclear material.

00:53.168 --> 00:54.368
Putting Oleg

00:54.436 --> 00:56.504
in a clinic would lead them
right to us.

00:56.571 --> 00:57.972
Dr. Levine.

00:58.040 --> 00:59.073
How did you get in here?

00:59.141 --> 01:00.908
My brother is sick.
I'm gonna call you

01:00.976 --> 01:02.443
an ambulance.
No.

01:02.511 --> 01:03.945
No one can know about this.

01:04.012 --> 01:06.681
(gasping):
No, no.

01:06.748 --> 01:08.282
What do you want from me?

01:08.350 --> 01:10.851
<i>You're a data analyst
for CTU.</i>

01:10.919 --> 01:13.020
You got access to all sorts
of good stuff.

01:13.088 --> 01:15.022
Yeah, but not unrestricted
access.

01:15.090 --> 01:17.124
Payout's got to be at least
six figures.

01:17.192 --> 01:18.492
You were undercover
for nearly two years

01:18.560 --> 01:19.961
with the Russian Mob.

01:20.028 --> 01:21.963
You're asking me to go back in?

01:22.030 --> 01:23.864
<i>Vladimir Laitanan was</i>

01:23.932 --> 01:25.533
completely obsessed with her.
It turned violent.

01:25.600 --> 01:26.667
Did he rape her?

01:26.735 --> 01:28.803
It looks like he tried
a couple of times.

01:28.870 --> 01:30.471
Can we talk
about this deal now?

01:30.539 --> 01:32.039
I wish it were that simple.

01:32.107 --> 01:33.507
Tie her up.
What?

01:33.575 --> 01:34.976
Look, you're making
a mistake.

01:35.043 --> 01:36.677
This is the chance
of a lifetimK]

01:36.745 --> 01:37.878
JACK:
This operation's over.

01:37.946 --> 01:39.880
Vladimir didn't take the bait.

01:39.948 --> 01:41.649
<i>Renee, it's Jack.</i>

01:41.717 --> 01:42.650
I know you can hear me.

01:42.718 --> 01:43.884
I'm on my way now.

01:43.952 --> 01:45.853
You don't want
to do this deal,

01:45.921 --> 01:47.488
then you might as well
just kill me,

01:47.556 --> 01:50.324
because this deal is
the only thing that I have.

01:50.392 --> 01:52.326
Do it!

01:52.394 --> 01:53.928
Pull the trigger!

01:56.665 --> 01:58.199
I had to be sure.

01:59.468 --> 02:00.901
CHLOE:
Jack, are you there?

02:00.969 --> 02:01.936
What's going on?

02:02.004 --> 02:03.404
She's in.

02:03.472 --> 02:04.805
They bought her cover.

02:06.000 --> 02:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
